  "body": "<p>Here are two for you since I neglected to post the one from last week on the blog, although it did appear on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/amytangerine/\">Instagram</a>. That and <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/amytangerine?sub_confirmation=1\">YouTube</a> seem to be more my jam lately, but I am prioritizing this blog as I have a lot of cool stuff to share with you.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/46d25a940a7870e7.png?v=1782533953\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/57d0d2e8b7080ac6.jpg?v=1782533956\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Thanks to Sian who shared the Kurt Vonnegut quote with me in the comments from a couple weeks ago!</p><p>I'm using this watercolor set from Michaels and I have finally tried a waterbrush and found one that I love by Tim Holtz/Ranger. If you have a favorite quote – silly, snarky or simple in its’ wisdom, please share in the comments!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}